  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assign1
    The purpose of this class is to create the menu that is displayed to the user, as well as the main method that enacts the display menu and all the cases based on the users choice.
    FoodItem
    The purpose of this class is to declare all the methods that will be called by the child classes as well as extra methods that check item codes and update quantity in stock as well.
    Fruit
    The purpose of this class is to call the Parent class FoodItem to finish the input of a FoodItem to include its orchard supplier by calling super()
    Inventory
    The purpose of this class is to use the inventory array of FoodItems to populate the inventory, buy, sell, and check item codes if it exists to either allow or disallow the user to enter that code
    Preserve
    The purpose of this class is to call the Parent class FoodItem to finish the input of a FoodItem to include its jar size in millilitres(mL) by calling super()
    Vegetable
    The purpose of this class is to call the Parent class FoodItem to finish the input of a FoodItem to include its farm supplier by calling super()
